RelatedSentence: Cobb County police today identified two men who were killed in a shootout Sunday evening that left two other people hospitalized .
Cobb County police today identified two men who were killed in a shootout Sunday evening that left two other people hospitalized .

Authorities confirmed that David Blount , 20 , of Smyrna , and Ryan Christopher Bobbitt , 24 , of Marietta , died in the shooting in the 2100 block of Cardell Road in Austell shortly after 6 p.m. I heard one shot out here , neighbors down the street said there was about six or eight shots , witness Julia Biddy told Channel 2 Action News .
